 {"id":"frankenjax-cmb","title":"Resolve complex select condition and clamp stubs in fj-lax arithmetic.rs (7 stubs)","description":"CONTEXT: 7 of the 14 stubs in fj-lax/src/arithmetic.rs are in Select and Clamp: 4x select with complex condition (lines ~1110, ~1162, ~1240, ~1315) say complex condition not yet implemented for select. 3x clamp with complex value/lo/hi (lines ~1401, ~1414, ~1426) say complex arithmetic not yet implemented.

ANALYSIS: Neither needs real implementation. JAX does NOT support complex conditions for select (must be bool) or complex clamp (no total order). These are correct errors with wrong wording that implies deferred work.

